PROCESSTYPE.name: Visitor CheckIn Flow
PROCESSTYPE.BPMNXML:
<definitions targetNamespace="http://www.activiti.org/test" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:activiti="http://activiti.org/bpmn" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL">
    <message name="injectListJSON" id="injectListJSON"/>
    <process isExecutable="true" name="Visitor CheckIn Flow" id="Visitor_CheckIn_Flow">
        <documentation>%3Cxml%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F1999%2Fxhtml%22%3E%3Cblock%20type%3D%22start%22%20id%3D%221%22%20deletable%3D%22false%22%20x%3D%220%22%20y%3D%220%22%3E%3Cfield%20name%3D%22NAME%22%3EVisitor%20CheckIn%20Flow%3C%2Ffield%3E%3Cnext%3E%3Cblock%20type%3D%22userTask%22%20id%3D%222%22%20inline%3D%22false%22%3E%3Cfield%20name%3D%22NAME%22%3ECheckIn%3C%2Ffield%3E%3Cnext%3E%3Cblock%20type%3D%22serviceTask%22%20id%3D%223%22%3E%3Cfield%20name%3D%22NAME%22%3ESend%20Notification%3C%2Ffield%3E%3Cfield%20name%3D%22factType%22%3ECREATE%3C%2Ffield%3E%3Cnext%3E%3Cblock%20type%3D%22userTask%22%20id%3D%224%22%20inline%3D%22false%22%3E%3Cfield%20name%3D%22NAME%22%3EThank%20You%3C%2Ffield%3E%3Cnext%3E%3Cblock%20type%3D%22end%22%20id%3D%225%22%20deletable%3D%22false%22%3E%3C%2Fblock%3E%3C%2Fnext%3E%3C%2Fblock%3E%3C%2Fnext%3E%3C%2Fblock%3E%3C%2Fnext%3E%3C%2Fblock%3E%3C%2Fnext%3E%3C%2Fblock%3E%3C%2Fxml%3E</documentation>
        <startEvent name="Visitor CheckIn Flow" id="start"/>
        <sequenceFlow targetRef="userTask1" sourceRef="start" id="flow1"/>
        <userTask activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" activiti:formKey="poi_CheckIn_form" name="CheckIn" id="userTask1"/>
        <boundaryEvent attachedToRef="userTask1" cancelActivity="false" name="Message" id="boundarymessage2">
            <messageEventDefinition messageRef="injectListJSON"/>
        </boundaryEvent>
        <sequenceFlow targetRef="serviceTask2" sourceRef="userTask1" id="flow3"/>
        <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.facts" name="Send Notification" id="serviceTask2">
            <extensionElements>
                <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
                    <activiti:string>poi_SendNotification_fact</activiti:string>
                </activiti:field>
                <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
                    <activiti:expression>${CREATEMap}</activiti:expression>
                </activiti:field>
            </extensionElements>
        </serviceTask>
        <sequenceFlow targetRef="userTask3" sourceRef="serviceTask2" id="flow4"/>
        <userTask activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" activiti:formKey="poi_ThankYou_form" name="Thank You" id="userTask3"/>
        <boundaryEvent attachedToRef="userTask3" cancelActivity="false" name="Message" id="boundarymessage5">
            <messageEventDefinition messageRef="injectListJSON"/>
        </boundaryEvent>
        <sequenceFlow targetRef="end" sourceRef="userTask3" id="flow6"/>
        <endEvent name="end" id="end"/>
    </process>
</definitions>
